    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>SARS-CoV-2 lineages prevalent in the first and second waves in Eastern Germany were different, with many new variants including four predominant lineages in the second wave, having been introduced into Eastern Germany between August to October 2020, indicating the major cause of the second wave was the introduction of new variants.</jats:p>",
